{"title":"车过临沂山区","authors":["雪兵"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":4,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"车过临沂山区"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的筑路工地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一方音乐天地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铿锵的音符，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随时都能拾起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当帐篷向前移动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的音符又喟然沉寂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山的轰鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推土机的喘息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激越的夯歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高亢的汽笛……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞旋在沸腾的工地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又埋进了坚实的路基。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里曾经进行过一次著名的战役。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁路在山中迂回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着当年的壕堑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着兵车的轨迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我贴耳细听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土里还响着——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲锋的号角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啸的弹雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀的交响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾的马蹄……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，那遥远的开拓足音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，这眼前的拚搏心律；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象乳汁注入清泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和谐地溶为一体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车从路轨辗过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏响两行长长的诗句——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让昨天和今天畅谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合奏一支腾飞之曲！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}